# B2 root-cause trace (round 2, PR head ad7cd462) — instrumented envtest run.
# Temporary klog.Infof probes added in a throwaway worktree at:
#   - instance_scale.go: DEBUG-RECREATE (recreation branch), DEBUG-URT (updateRestartTracking enter/exit)
#   - instance_status.go: DEBUG-US (updateStatus: newStatus/instance/liveClone counts + isReset + final)
# Scenario: seed RestartCount=5, LastRestartTime=11min ago (>10min stable threshold), then crash a pod.
# Intended: counter resets to 1. Observed: transiently persists 1, then a stale-cache reconcile
# clobbers it back to 5 permanently (read-modify-write race).

